  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>It would be awesome if notifications in IRCCloud synced across devices and even the web app. So if I dismiss a notification on my phone, it will clear on my tablet and on the web app too.</p>

<p>I believe this is done with Google Cloud Messaging? <a href="http://developer.android.com/google/gcm/">http://developer.android.com/google/gcm/</a></p>

<p>Just an idea, I don't know if its feasible to implement.</p>

<p>Thanks!</p>
      </div>
