  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>Unfortunately the only way to clear a notification from the web app is to mark the channel as read, which is not what the user would expect to happen when dismissing a notification from their phone.  Syncing between Android devices might be possible, though.  Thanks for the suggestion.</p>
      </div>
